summary: ACCIDENT ON MARCH 25TH, 2002.  THE OTHER DRIVER RAN A STOP SIGN GOING 10-15 MPH.  I WAS GOING 45 MPH.  HIS TOYOTA CAMRY STRUCK MY JEEP LIBERTY ON THE FRONT PASSENGER SIDE.  THE IMPACT TORE THE FRONT TIRE OFF AND RIPPED OUT THE RIGHT FRONT SUSPENSION.  THERE WAS NO AIR BAG DEPLOYMENT.  I SLAMMED INTO THE DASH AND HAD SEVERE BRUISES ON MY KNEES.*JB
